snippet.title: Mobile Suit Gundam: Extreme VS-Force - Launch Trailer | Vita
snippet.description:
Take part in the Gundam Extreme universe with MOBILE SUIT GUNDAM EXTREME VS-FORCE. All of the DLC is included in this digital edition. Available now for the PlayStation®Vita from the PlayStation Store! https://store.playstation.com/#!/en-us/games/mobile-suit-gundam-extreme-vs-force-bundle/cid=UP0700-PCSE00915_00-VSTABUNDLE000000
